description: Redevelopment to provide 220 affordable (social rented and intermediate) dwellings and associated amenity space, car parking and cycle parking, and creation of new park to the east of the site (known as Rowley Gardens within the Master Plan). The scheme comprises the erection of three blocks ranging in height from 7 storeys to 10 storeys. (Conditions 5, 6, 14, 25, 38, 40, 43 and 45 refer)
